{
  "nbformat": 4,
  "nbformat_minor": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "kernelspec": {
      "name": "maxima",
      "display_name": "Maxima",
      "language": "maxima"
    },
    "aximar": {}
  },
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# Phase Portraits and Fixed Point Classification\n\nThis notebook explores the relationship between eigenvalues of a linear system's matrix and the qualitative behaviour of its phase portrait. We classify fixed points as stable nodes, saddle points, spirals, and centres, then apply the same tools to a nonlinear Lotka-Volterra system via linearization.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "load(\"numerics\")$\nload(\"ax-plots\")$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 106,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Linear Systems\n\nFor a linear system $\\dot{\\mathbf{x}} = A\\mathbf{x}$, the eigenvalues of $A$ completely determine the phase portrait near the origin. We work through each case.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "### Stable Node [S+N]\n\nWhen both eigenvalues are real and negative, all trajectories converge to the origin along the eigenvector directions. The system is asymptotically stable.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Stable node: both eigenvalues negative */\nA_node : matrix([-2, 0], [0, -1])$\nevals_node : eigenvalues(A_node);\n\nprint(\"Eigenvalues:\", evals_node[1])$\nprint(\"Both negative real => stable node\")$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 107,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "[[-2,-1],[1,1]]\nEigenvalues: [-2,-1]\nBoth negative real => stable node"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Phase portrait: trajectories converge to origin */\nax_draw2d(\n  ax_vector_field(-2*x, -y, x, -3, 3, y, -3, 3),\n  ax_streamline(-2*x, -y, x, -3, 3, y, -3, 3),\n  title=\"Stable Node\",\n  xlabel=\"x\", ylabel=\"y\",\n  aspect_ratio=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 108,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "application/x-maxima-plotly": [
