    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "### Unstable Spiral\n\nWhen the real part of complex eigenvalues is positive, trajectories spiral outward from the origin.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Unstable spiral: complex eigenvalues with positive real part */\nA_uspiral : matrix([1, 2], [-2, 1])$\nevals_uspiral : eigenvalues(A_uspiral);\n\nprint(\"Eigenvalues:\", evals_uspiral[1])$\nprint(\"Complex with Re > 0 => unstable spiral\")$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 113,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "[[1-2*%i,2*%i+1],[1,1]]\nEigenvalues: [1-2*%i,2*%i+1]\nComplex with Re > 0 => unstable spiral"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Unstable spiral: trajectories wind outward */\nax_draw2d(\n  ax_vector_field(x + 2*y, -2*x + y, x, -3, 3, y, -3, 3),\n  ax_streamline(x + 2*y, -2*x + y, x, -3, 3, y, -3, 3),\n  title=\"Unstable Spiral\",\n  xlabel=\"x\", ylabel=\"y\",\n  aspect_ratio=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 114,
      "outputs": [
        {
